payments to insurance

19:42.714 --> 19:48.086 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
companies to cover out-of-pocket
costs and
deductibles for low-income
consumers.

19:48.120 --> 19:52.724 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The Obama administration lost a
crucial court
ruling that concluded those
payments were

19:52.758 --> 19:57.462 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
not constitutional unless
authorized by Congress.

19:57.496 --> 20:02.467 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Seven million people, more than
half of those
covered through the insurance
exchanges, qualify

20:02.501 --> 20:04.336 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
