23:03.949 --> 23:05.951 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, the
exchanges, some of
them could collapse?

23:05.984 --> 23:06.952 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
That's what...

23:06.985 --> 23:08.353 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(CROSSTALK)

23:08.387 --> 23:10.088 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ROBERT LASZEWSKI: I doubt you
would see the
exchanges collapse.

23:10.122 --> 23:14.126 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We get the into the weeds of how
all this
works, but the bottom line is,
the insurance

23:14.159 --> 23:18.964 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
