increase the
rates for all 20 million in the
pool.

23:18.997 --> 23:21.032 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It would make things even more
expensive.

23:21.066 --> 23:25.036 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We would have even fewer healthy
people, and
which would, in turn, make
things even more

23:25.070 --> 23:27.005 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
