23:27.038 --> 23:30.041 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It continues to make things
unstable.

23:30.075 --> 23:35.547 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Right now, Judy, typically, a
family of four,
mom and dad age 40, right now,
would have

23:35.580 --> 23:40.919 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
