get subsidies.

23:43.989 --> 23:45.924 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And half the people don't get
subsidies.

23:45.957 --> 23:52.264 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, what this would is, it would
just tend
-- it would make this far worse.

23:52.297 --> 23:56.101 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
