24:23.495 --> 24:27.532 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Why would we make an unstable
situation even
much worse?

24:27.566 --> 24:30.135 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: How do you see
this playing
out?

24:30.168 --> 24:35.207 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
