political perspective.

25:05.103 --> 25:09.508 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So this is all about resolving
the budget
impasse and all about resolving
the repeal

25:09.541 --> 25:12.677 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
