Republicans
are dealing with.

25:12.711 --> 25:16.314 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And until that's -- those two
things are resolved,
this is going to be an issue
that people are

25:16.348 --> 25:17.315 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
going to be worrying about.

25:17.349 --> 25:18.783 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: It's a tough one.

25:18.817 --> 25:21.920 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ROBERT LASZEWSKI: Yes, it is.

25:21.953 --> 25:29.027 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Robert Laszewski,
