in France.

30:22.453 --> 30:34.065 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: More than a
decade- and-a-half
into the U.S. war in
Afghanistan, the country

30:34.098 --> 30:36.835 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
