from Chicago.

37:37.488 --> 37:39.023 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
And welcome to you both.

37:39.056 --> 37:42.693 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So, 100 days, we're coming up on
it this Saturday.

37:42.727 --> 37:46.564 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Amy, during the campaign, the
