he was saying
it's a ridiculous standard.

37:51.535 --> 37:52.937 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

37:52.970 --> 37:53.638 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
AMY WALTER, The Cook Political
Report: Right,
an arbitrary standard.

37:53.671 --> 37:54.505 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: But what is it?

37:54.538 --> 37:55.506 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
