37:55.539 --> 37:56.507 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
How much attention should we
give it?

37:56.540 --> 37:58.276 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
AMY WALTER: Yes, it's a very
good question.

37:58.309 --> 38:01.379 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
You know, normally, president,
especially
-- first-term presidents start
off in their

38:01.412 --> 38:04.548 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
